Introduction

Lín Wéixī, better known as Kelly, is a Taiwanese singer under TR Entertainment. She is the Lead Vocalist and Visual of the girl group TRI.BE.

In March 2020, Kelly participated as a contestant on the Chinese survival show "Youth With You 2", where she faced elimination in episode 10 and secured the 64th position.

On September 10, 2020, Kelly was officially introduced as the sixth member of TRI.BE.
